data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! Step into luxury with the 2 story Catherine floorplan. This spectacular home is complete with 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, Office Room, Loft and 2 car garage. The heart of the home has a center island and overlooks the dining and family room, which is great for entertaining. The owner suite features a large bedroom and elegant owner bathroom with his and her sinks, shower and a roomy walk-in closet. The community offers residents luxury amenities in a great location and easy access to major Florida highways, such as SR 535, I-4, and US 192. Storey Creek amenities include a fully-equipped fitness center, clubhouse, resort-style swimming pool, tennis courts and playground. This community will also offer residents a great location to explore nearby shopping, dining and entertainment.
